videos.description: Creighton's Ty-Shon Alexander shakes a defender and kisses glass on the spinning jumper to put the Bluejays up 3 with less than 20 seconds left.

videos.description: Marquette's Markus Howard splashes a step-back 3 in overtime to put the Golden Eagles up 6 over Creighton.

videos.description: Markus Howard breaks a Big East record with 53 points as Marquette soars to a thrilling 106-104 overtime victory over Creighton.
